*Prekini* ga! (Stop him!)
Ona je *prekinula* vezu. (She broke up the relationship.)
On je *prekinuo* svoju vezu sa njom. (He ended his relationship with her.)
Niko nije mogao da *prekine* njihovu ljubav. (No one could break up their love.)
Oni su *prekinuli* razgovor. (They interrupted the conversation.)
Ona je *prekinula* da jede. (She stopped eating.)